text: This section describes the Amazon S3 collection and forwarding agents. These agents are available in batch and real-time workflow configurations. The Amazon S3 agents collect and forward batches of files from specified buckets and regions in Amazon. Open The section contains the following subsections: Amazon Profile Amazon S3 Collection Agent Amazon S3 Forwarding Agent
